Calny Inc director and formerpresident and chief executive officer said he is resigning fromCalny's board because of the company's recently announcedlawsuit against Pepsico Inc &lt;PEP> and its La PetiteBoulangerie.    In a statement, Larvive said the suit is a "lose-lose"situation for Calny, which is the only franchisee for La PetiteBoulangerie and is the largest francisee of PepsiCo's Taco BellCorp. Reuter&#3;